OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FSome early low cloud, mist and
OL,6,Ffog clearing through the morning to
OL,7,Fleave a dry, mild and bright afternoon
OL,8,Fon Thursday with some hazy sunshine.
OL,9,
OL,10,CTonight:FA generally mild night with
OL,11,Fcloud thickening from the west into
OL,12,Fthe evening, bringing a few outbreaks
OL,13,Fof rain into the north and west by
OL,14,Fdawn on Friday.
OL,15,
OL,16,CFriday:FCloudier on Friday, with light
OL,17,Frain during the morning turning
OL,18,Fheavier and more persistent through
OL,19,Fthe afternoon. Feeling much cooler by
OL,20,Fday under widespread cloud.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
